<h3><b>Solution</b></h3>
<p>Kita diminta untuk decode pesan base64 diatas yang nantinya akan berupa file ekstensi elf, lalu jalankan file maka didapatkan string untuk requests ke link https://ringzer0ctf.com/challenges/15/[your_string], dalam waktu 3 detik</p>

import requests
import re
import base64
import os

file_elf = open("fileelf.elf","wb")
    
with requests.Session() as session:
    payload = {"username":"your-username",#username
               "password":"your-password"}#password
    URL = "https://ringzer0ctf.com/login"
    post = session.post(URL, data=payload)
    r = session.get("https://ringzer0ctf.com/challenges/15")
    challenge = re.findall('----- BEGIN Elf Message -----<br />\r\n\t\t(.*?)<br />\r\n\t\t----- End Elf Message -----', r.text)[0]
    list_decode = []
    list_decode.append(challenge)
    for i in list_decode:
        a = base64.b64decode(i)
        list_decode.append(a)
        if "tini" in str(list_decode[-1]):
            break
    file_elf.write(list_decode[-1][::-1])
    file_elf.close()
